(16, 1, '2015-07-10 07:44:43', '2015-07-10 07:44:43', 'Nearly two decades of experience joining the same way with the mordenisation of the construction and mining industries, we have engaged in importing heavy equipments such as crane, excavator, bulldozer, dumtruck... In cooperation with Viet Nhat CMT, the exclusive distributor of the Japanese Sumitomo Construction Machinery brand, we have now a wide range of excellent brand new hydraulic excavators and asphalt pavers for your choice.', 'Construction Machines', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'construction-machines', '', '', '2015-07-10 07:44:43', '2015-07-10 07:44:43', '', 0, 'http://localhost/ntcorp/?p=16', 0, 'post', '', 0),
