(18, 1, '2015-07-10 07:54:31', '2015-07-10 07:54:31', 'Managed by a team of well-experinced journalists and professionals, we take care of all your needs for public relations and communications to the outside world, in the most brilliant ways with the most updated media technologies. While offering simple services of ad booking, press releases, our priority is given to overall consulting, content production and crisis management.', 'Intro', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'intro', '', '', '2015-07-10 07:54:31', '2015-07-10 07:54:31', '', 0, 'http://localhost/ntcorp/?p=18', 0, 'post', '', 0),
