(20, 1, '2015-07-10 08:34:48', '2015-07-10 08:34:48', 'We are excited to launch our new company and product Goran. After being featured in too many magazines to mention and having created an online stir, we know that Goran is going to be big. You may have seen us in the Dinosaurs’ Den where we were we told that we didn’t need them because we were already doing it so well ourselves, so that’s what we have continued to do. We also hope to win Startup Fictional Business of the Year this Year.\r\n\r\nBrowse our site and see for yourself why you need Goran.\r\n\r\nHere are some of the fantastic things people have had to say about Goran:\r\n<blockquote>It’s just brilliant. I will recommend Goran to everyone I know! <cite>– A. Girl.</cite></blockquote>\r\n<blockquote>I’m really glad these guys got Goran out there. I’ve bought it and now think perhaps I should have invested! <cite>– A. Dinosaur.</cite></blockquote>\r\nHere are just some of the magazine reviews we have had:\r\n<blockquote>Goran. That says it all really. ★★★★\r\n<cite>– One of the Magazines</cite></blockquote>\r\n<blockquote>What a product. Why didn’t someone think of it sooner? ★★★★★\r\n<cite>– Another Magazine</cite></blockquote>\r\n<blockquote>Get out there and buy it if you’re a customer and stock it if you’re a retailer – you’d be mad not to! ★★★★★\r\n<cite>– Some other Magazine</cite></blockquote>', 'About Us', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'about-us', '', '', '2015-07-10 08:50:13', '2015-07-10 08:50:13', '', 0, 'http://localhost/ntcorp/?page_id=20', 0, 'page', '', 0),
(21, 1, '2015-07-10 08:34:48', '2015-07-10 08:34:48', '<h2>It happens millions of times each week – a customer receives a drink from a Starbucks barista – but each interaction is unique.</h2>\r\n<img class="image_left summary_image" src="http://globalassets.starbucks.com/assets/43742c946e044977b5a9891e234e8eb9.jpg" alt="Store front of original Pike Place store" />\r\n\r\nIt’s just a moment in time – just one hand reaching over the counter to present a cup to another outstretched hand.\r\n\r\nBut it’s a connection.\r\n\r\nWe make sure everything we do honors that connection – from our commitment to the highest quality coffee in the world, to the way we engage with our customers and communities <a href="http://www.starbucks.com/responsibility" shape="rect">to do business responsibly</a>.\r\n\r\nFrom <a href="http://www.starbucks.com/about-us/our-heritage" shape="rect">our beginnings</a> as a single store over forty years ago, in every place that we’ve been, and every place that we touch, we''ve tried to make it a little better than we found it.', 'About Us', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '20-revision-v1', '', '', '2015-07-10 08:34:48', '2015-07-10 08:34:48', '', 20, 'http://localhost/ntcorp/20-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(22, 1, '2015-07-10 08:50:05', '2015-07-10 08:50:05', 'We are excited to launch our new company and product Goran. After being featured in too many magazines to mention and having created an online stir, we know that Goran is going to be big. You may have seen us in the Dinosaurs’ Den where we were we told that we didn’t need them because we were already doing it so well ourselves, so that’s what we have continued to do. We also hope to win Startup Fictional Business of the Year this Year.\n\nBrowse our site and see for yourself why you need Goran.\n\nHere are some of the fantastic things people have had to say about Goran:\n<blockquote>It’s just brilliant. I will recommend Goran to everyone I know! <cite>– A. Girl.</cite></blockquote>\n<blockquote>I’m really glad these guys got Goran out there. I’ve bought it and now think perhaps I should have invested! <cite>– A. Dinosaur.</cite></blockquote>\nHere are just some of the magazine reviews we have had:\n<blockquote>Goran. That says it all really. ★★★★\n<cite>– One of the Magazines</cite></blockquote>\n<blockquote>What a product. Why didn’t someone think of it sooner? ★★★★★\n<cite>– Another Magazine</cite></blockquote>\n<blockquote>Get out there and buy it if you’re a customer and stock it if you’re a retailer – you’d be mad not to! ★★★★★\n<cite>– Some other Magazine</cite></blockquote>', 'About Us', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '20-autosave-v1', '', '', '2015-07-10 08:50:05', '2015-07-10 08:50:05', '', 20, 'http://localhost/ntcorp/20-autosave-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
